## Quick Reference: Dataview Patterns

### Project Freshness Query
```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "Project",
  round((date(today) - file.mtime).days) as "Days Stale",
  choice((date(today) - file.mtime).days < 7, "Fresh",
    choice((date(today) - file.mtime).days < 14, "Stale", "Rotting")) as "Status"
FROM "Projects"
WHERE type = "project"
SORT (date(today) - file.mtime).days DESC
```

### Tech Stack Usage Query
```dataviewjs
const projects = dv.pages('"Projects"').where(p => p.type === "project");
const techMap = new Map();

projects.forEach(p => {
  const stack = p["tech-stack"] || [];
  stack.forEach(tech => {
    const name = String(tech).replace(/\[\[.*\||\]\]/g, '');
    techMap.set(name, (techMap.get(name) || 0) + 1);
  });
});

dv.table(["Technology", "Projects Using"],
  [...techMap.entries()].sort((a,b) => b[1] - a[1]));
```

### Task Completion This Week
```dataview
TASK
FROM "Projects" OR "Journal"
WHERE completed AND completion >= date(today) - dur(7 days)
SORT completion DESC
LIMIT 20
```

